Package food.model.input

Interface FoodApi

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    FoodApiImpl
    public interface FoodApi
    Interface representing the input API (Food-Database). In previous versions of program, Facade interacted directly with the FoodDatabase implementations. This has been replaced with this facade which interacts with both the cache and the API strategies.
